public GeckoSession.PromptDelegate.PromptResponse confirm(int selection)
        Confirms this prompt, returning the selected button to content.
        Parameters:
        selection - An int representing the selected button, must be one of GeckoSession.PromptDelegate.ButtonPrompt.Type.
